            "title": "茶飲股借勢炒上 蜜雪破頂 茶百道飆逾12%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">乘著霸王茶姬於美國IPO傳以上限定價的好消息，在港上市茶飲股齊借勢炒上。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250303_FI_source-ap_MIXUE-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250303_FI_source-ap_MIXUE-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">蜜雪集團(02097)創新高；茶百道(02555)午後最多曾飆12.86%，截至下午約2時07分報8.95元，仍漲11.74%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">蜜雪則早在上午開始揚升，午後續於高位徘徊，最高曾見477.8元，飆8.69%；暫報475.2元，仍升8.1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另一隻茶飲股古茗(01364)也見5日新高，暫報18.22元，升7.56%。奈雪的茶(02150)午後發力，暫報0.99元，升6.45%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14861715-%e8%8c%b6%e9%a3%b2%e8%82%a1%e5%80%9f%e5%8b%a2%e7%82%92%e4%b8%8a-%e8%9c%9c%e9%9b%aa%e7%a0%b4%e9%a0%82-%e8%8c%b6%e7%99%be%e9%81%93%e9%a3%86%e9%80%be12",
