        {
            "title": "台積電首季純利按年升60.3% 勝預期",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">台積電公布，今年首季稅後純利3615.64億元(新台幣‧下同)，按年升60.3%，勝市場預期。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：台積電官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230717-160018_20230717_fi_TSMC_fb_source-web_-1-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：台積電官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230717-160018_20230717_fi_TSMC_fb_source-web_-1-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：台積電官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內集團合併營收約8392.54億元，按年升41.6%。營業毛利4933.95億元，較去年同期提升56.9%；營業盈利4070.81億元，按年增長63.5%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">集團首季營業毛利率達58.8%，較去年同期的53.1%提升了5.7點；營業淨利率48.5%，也較去年同期的42%提升6.5點；純利率43.1%，較去年同期的38%提高5.1點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">奈米製程出貨佔台積電今年首季晶圓銷售金額的22%，5奈米製程出貨佔全季晶圓銷售金額的36%；7奈米製程出貨則佔全季晶圓銷售金額的15%。總體而言，先進製程(包含7奈米及更先進製程)的營收達到全季晶圓銷售金額的73%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14861677-%e5%8f%b0%e7%a9%8d%e9%9b%bb%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%8760-3-%e5%8b%9d%e9%a0%90%e6%9c%9f",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241017_FI_source-web_tsmc-3.jpg.webp",
